  <h1>Privacy Policy – VM Personalized Gifts</h1>
  <p>Effective date: July 2025</p>

  <p>VM Personalized Gifts ("we", "our", or "us") operates the Etsy store <a href="https://vmpersonalizedgifts.etsy.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://vmpersonalizedgifts.etsy.com</a> and uses automated tools to post on Pinterest. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We do not collect any personal data through this app or website. Any data you provide through Etsy or Pinterest is managed by those platforms according to their privacy policies.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Since we do not collect personal information directly, we do not use your data for any purpose.</p>

  <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
  <p>We do not use cookies or tracking technologies on this website.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use Etsy and Pinterest platforms which have their own privacy policies. Please review their policies to understand how your data is handled on those services.</p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to review, update, or delete any personal information you provide directly to Etsy or Pinterest.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:icoman2807@gmail.com">icoman2807@gmail.com</a>.</p>

